citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:00pm on 13-SEP-
21. Upon arrival to the facility, the licensee was contacted but because of prior obligations, no responsible adult would be
available for an inspection within 60 minutes.
